songs.title: Especial, loved and Nice People
songs.lyrics:
You're special to me, this is a nice friendship
I know I'm not very good for many

I met a lot of people, but few have cared about me
You helped me overcome, this is a nice friendship

I know this is not the farewell, but my words are expressed here

Listen out!!! They are special for me
Seriously, you are and will continue to be

You make me feel something, something nice
They make me feel good

I'm going to disappear a few days, of everything
Maybe you miss me, but do not forget my face
It will only be a few days

The world consumes me, I go out
I feel out

Listen out!!! They are special for me
Seriously, you are and will continue to be

Maybe you miss me

It's you? you helped me
It's you? you took me out
It's you? you helped me
It's you? you took me out

GOODBYE EVERYONE
